doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title F5 and IBM are Boundless - ISC 2022

        // Favicon
        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        // Bootstrap Icons
        link(href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.5.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css', rel='stylesheet')

        // Google fonts
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Merriweather+Sans:400,700', rel='stylesheet')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Merriweather:400,300,300italic,400italic,700,700italic', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

        // SimpleLightbox plugin CSS
        link(href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/SimpleLightbox/2.1.0/simpleLightbox.min.css', rel='stylesheet')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-light.fixed-top.py-3
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                a.navbar-brand(href='#page-top') Home
                button.navbar-toggler.navbar-toggler-right(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    span.navbar-toggler-icon
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ms-auto.my-2.my-lg-0
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#about') About
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#services') Services
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#resources') Resources
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#contact') Contact
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='/diag') Diagnostic Demo

        // Masthead
        header.masthead
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.h-100.vh-100
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.h-100.align-items-center.justify-content-center.text-center
                    .col-lg-8.align-self-end
                        h1.text-white.font-weight-bold F5 and IBM
                        hr.divider
                    .col-lg-8.align-self-baseline
                        p.text-white-50.mb-5
                            | the partnership for enterprise cloud
                        a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl(href='#about') Find Out More

        // About
        section#about.page-section.bg-primary
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.h-100.vh-100
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.h-100.justify-content-center
                    .col-lg-8.text-center
                        h2.text-white.mt-0 We've got what you need!
                        hr.divider.divider-light
                        p.text-white-75.mb-4
                            | IBM cloud services cater to enterprise. F5 application delivery and security services, running in IBM cloud, can move your cloud projects from planned to successful. With an extensive list of shared industry leading customers, nobody is better poised to understand what you need and get you to there. Avoid the pitfalls and make it work with F5 and IBM.
                        a.btn.btn-light.btn-xl(href='#services') Get Started!

        // Services
        section#services.page-section
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.h-100.vh-100
                h2.text-center.mt-0 What do you need?
                hr.divider
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5
                    .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                        .mt-5
                            .mb-2
                                i.bi-diagram-3.fs-1.text-primary
                            h3.h4.mb-2 Enterprise Lift<br/>and Shift
                            p.text-muted.mb-0
                              | Take advantage of the<br/>IBM global infrastructure<br/>for your applications.<br/>We'll work with you<br/>to make your cloud<br/>migration a success.
                    .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                        .mt-5
                            .mb-2
                                i.bi-bank.fs-1.text-primary
                            h3.h4.mb-2 Industry Clouds
                            p.text-muted.mb-0
                              | From financial standards<br/>compliance, to telco<br/>subscriber services,<br/>to healthcare solutions,<br/>we understand how<br/> to do the hard<br/>work in cloud.
                    .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                        .mt-5
                            .mb-2
                                i.bi-gear.fs-1.text-primary
                            h3.h4.mb-2 Private Enterprise<br/>AI Solutions
                            p.text-muted.mb-0
                              | Connect your application<br/>data and analysis<br/>to Watson securely.<br/>Big data doesn't have<br/>to mean big exposure.
                    .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                        .mt-5
                            .mb-2
                                i.bi-stack.fs-1.text-primary
                            h3.h4.mb-2 Next Generation<br/>Edge Cloud
                            p.text-muted.mb-0
                              | IBM Satellite delivers<br/>the power of OpenShift<br/>whereever you need it.<br/>F5 Volterra extends application<br/>services between clusters,<br/>data centers, and<br/>branches seamlessly.
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.justify-content-center.pt-4
                    .col-lg-8.text-center
                        a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl(href='#resources') Dig Deeper!
        // Portfolio
        section#resources.page-section
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.h-100.vh-100
                #portfolio
                    .container.container-fluid
                        .row.g-0
                            .col-lg-4.col-sm-6
                                a.portfolio-box(href='assets/img/portfolio/fullsize/1.gif', title='F5 BIG-IP in IBM VPC')
                                    img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/1.jpg', alt='...')
                                    .portfolio-box-caption
                                        .project-category.text-white-50
                                            | Enterprise Lift and Shift and Industry Cloud
                                        .project-name
                                            | F5 BIG-IP in IBM VPC
                            .col-lg-4.col-sm-6
                                a.portfolio-box(href='assets/img/portfolio/fullsize/2.gif', title='Volterra CE Sites in IBM Cloud')
                                    img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/2.jpg', alt='...')
                                    .portfolio-box-caption
                                        .project-category.text-white-50
                                            | Secure Access to Cloud Resources
                                        .project-name
                                            | Volterra CE Sites in IBM Cloud
                            .col-lg-4.col-sm-6
                                a.portfolio-box(href='assets/img/portfolio/fullsize/3.gif', title='Volterra ADN with IBM Satellite')
                                    img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/3.jpg', alt='...')
                                    .portfolio-box-caption
                                        .project-category.text-white-50
                                            | Edge Cloud Services
                                        .project-name
                                            | Volterra ADN with IBM Satellite
                        .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.justify-content-center.pt-4
                                .col-lg-8.text-center
                                    a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl(href='#contact') Let's Get to Planning
        // Contact
        section#contact.page-section.bg-primary
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.h-100.vh-100
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.justify-content-center
                    .col-lg-8.col-xl-6.text-white.text-center
                        h2.mt-0 Ready to start your project?
                        hr.divider
                        p.text-white-75.mb-5
                            | Send us a message and we will get back to you as soon as possible!
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.justify-content-center.pt-4
                    .col-lg-8.text-center
                        a.btn.btn-light.btn-xl(href='mailto:ibmcloudteam@f5.com', target='_blank') Email the F5 IBM Cloud Team

        // Footer
        footer.bg-light.py-5
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                .small.text-center.text-muted
                    | Copyright &copy; 2021 - F5 Networks

        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')

        // SimpleLightbox plugin JS
        script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/SimpleLightbox/2.1.0/simpleLightbox.min.js')

        // Core theme JS
        script(src='js/scripts.js')
